# 🚀 Project Sentinel

## Enterprise-Grade Incremental Data Ingestion Pipeline using Databricks Auto Loader & Delta Lake

---

# 📖 Project Overview

Project Sentinel is an enterprise-grade incremental data ingestion pipeline developed using **Databricks Auto Loader**, **PySpark**, and **Delta Lake** following the **Medallion Architecture (Bronze → Silver → Gold)**.

The pipeline automatically detects newly arrived transaction files, ingests only new data using checkpointing, applies data quality checks, transforms raw data into trusted datasets, and generates business-ready analytical insights.

The project demonstrates modern Data Engineering concepts including incremental data ingestion, schema enforcement, schema evolution, late data handling, Delta Lake ACID transactions, monitoring, logging, and SQL-based analytics.

---

# 🎯 Project Objectives

- Build an incremental data ingestion pipeline using Databricks Auto Loader.
- Implement the Medallion Architecture (Bronze, Silver, Gold).
- Perform data cleaning, validation, and deduplication.
- Demonstrate Schema Enforcement and Schema Evolution.
- Handle late-arriving data efficiently.
- Generate business-ready analytical datasets.
- Monitor pipeline execution using logs and monitoring reports.
- Simulate a production-ready Data Engineering workflow.

