---

# ▶️ Notebook Execution Order

Run the notebooks in the following order:

| Step | Notebook | Description |
|------|----------|-------------|
| 1 | 01_Data_Generation.ipynb | Generate sample retail transaction dataset |
| 2 | 02_Bronze_AutoLoader.ipynb | Incremental ingestion using Databricks Auto Loader |
| 3 | 03_Silver_Layer.ipynb | Data cleaning, validation and deduplication |
| 4 | 04_Gold_Layer.ipynb | Generate business-ready Gold tables |
| 5 | 05_SQL_Analytics.ipynb | SQL analysis on Bronze, Silver and Gold tables |
| 6 | 06_Schema_Evolution_Demo.ipynb | Demonstrate automatic schema evolution |
| 7 | 07_Monitoring.ipynb | Pipeline monitoring and data quality metrics |
| 8 | 08_Pipeline_Logs.ipynb | Pipeline execution logging |
| 9 | 09_Failure_Handling.ipynb | Demonstrate failure handling and rescued data |

---

# 🥉 Bronze Layer

The Bronze layer ingests raw transaction files using **Databricks Auto Loader**.

### Features

- Incremental File Ingestion
- Auto Loader (cloudFiles)
- Schema Enforcement
- Checkpointing
- Ingestion Timestamp
- Raw Delta Table Storage

---

# 🥈 Silver Layer

The Silver layer transforms raw data into clean and trusted datasets.

### Features

- Remove Duplicate Records
- Handle Null Values
- Data Type Standardization
- Data Validation
- Data Quality Checks
- Clean Delta Tables

---

# 🥇 Gold Layer

The Gold layer generates business-ready analytical datasets.

### Generated KPIs

- Top Products
- Top Customers
- Payment Distribution
- Revenue Analysis

---

# 📊 SQL Analytics

The project includes SQL-based business analysis on Delta tables.

Example analyses include:

- Revenue Analysis
- Product Performance
- Customer Analysis
- Payment Method Distribution
- Sales Summary

---

# 📈 Monitoring & Logging

The project includes dedicated notebooks for monitoring pipeline execution.

Implemented features:

- Pipeline Monitoring Dashboard
- Pipeline Execution Logs
- Data Quality Report
- Success/Failure Status Tracking
- Record Count Validation

---

# 🔄 Schema Management

The project demonstrates modern schema management techniques.

### Implemented

- ✅ Schema Enforcement
- ✅ Schema Evolution
- ✅ Automatic Detection of New Columns
- ✅ Late Data Handling

